WEBVTT

00:00:00.367 --> 00:00:03.436
The Rater and Employee must actively engage in reviewing

00:00:03.503 --> 00:00:06.373
achievable performance standards used in the Employee's

00:00:06.439 --> 00:00:08.141
performance plan.

00:00:08.208 --> 00:00:10.910
The purpose is to ensure consistency with Department

00:00:10.977 --> 00:00:14.547
measurements such as organizational goals for a facility.

00:00:14.614 --> 00:00:17.183
Sometimes the Department will modify performance standards

00:00:17.250 --> 00:00:19.586
within the appraisal period.

00:00:19.652 --> 00:00:20.487
When this happens,

00:00:20.553 --> 00:00:24.124
the Employee must be made aware of the modifications before he

00:00:24.190 --> 00:00:28.228
or she is held responsible for the changed standards.

00:00:28.294 --> 00:00:31.498
Also, the Employee will not be rated against the modified

00:00:31.564 --> 00:00:33.967
standards for at least 90 days.


